description: Chef Jorge is taking his natural culinary talents to the streets of Miami with his delicious selection of tostones and wraps stuffed with authentic Cuban comfort food. The mouthwatering menu includes a few tasty vegan options too. If you’re craving Cuban cuisine for your next event or party, The Stuffed Cuban truck will come straight to your home or office and serve your guests a taste of the best.
name: The Stuffed Cuban
